column5: Great report - and AWESOME fish for a rookie!
Awesome stuff man, hope to have a smile that big on my yap next weekend!
Nice we were out and off the lake at 9  went 5/7  mostly a spoon bite. Lost the biggest fish of the season so far and kept a few for the smoker  Hellava season so far in the west end
It's gonna be a good one I think Burned a few big ones the other night same setup
Nice fish guys. Looks like the bite was on for all of us before the rain hit.

Your couple of hours this morning was more productive than some guys entire season on Lake O, me included. Good going my man. But you have that rookie spoiled, he's going to expect that every outing unless you explained it only happens sometimes once in a lifetime for big Kings like you had.
Amazing average size there.  Amazing morning there!
